quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega, ntiwamenye ingene Imana yawe Rurema Allah Yagize beninzovu!"
  105,2,"Umugambi wabo mubi, ntiyawugize impfagusa ukaburizwamwo!"
  105,3,"Iraheza Ibarungikira inyoni ziri mu migwimigwi;"
  105,4,"Zibatera amabuye yokeje, ziraheza zirabahonya."
  105,5,"Maze Ibagira nk’ivyatsi vyarishijwe n'intungwa hanyuma iravyuza, iraheza ibita ari amahenehene."
